11518 &LaneMaskComposeSequences[24], // to sub12
11519 &LaneMaskComposeSequences[26], // to sub13
11520 &LaneMaskComposeSequences[28], // to sub14
11521 &LaneMaskComposeSequences[30] // to sub15
11522 };
11523
11524LaneBitmask R600GenRegisterInfo::composeSubRegIndexLaneMaskImpl(unsigned IdxA, LaneBitmask LaneMask) const {
11525 --IdxA; assert(IdxA < 16 && "Subregister index out of bounds");
11526 LaneBitmask Result;
11527 for (const MaskRolOp *Ops = CompositeSequences[IdxA]; Ops->Mask.any(); ++Ops) {
11528 LaneBitmask::Type M = LaneMask.getAsInteger() & Ops->Mask.getAsInteger();
11529 if (unsigned S = Ops->RotateLeft)
11530 Result |= LaneBitmask((M << S) | (M >> (LaneBitmask::BitWidth - S)));
11531 else
11532 Result |= LaneBitmask(M);
11533 }
11534 return Result;
11535}
11536
11537LaneBitmask R600GenRegisterInfo::reverseComposeSubRegIndexLaneMaskImpl(unsigned IdxA, LaneBitmask LaneMask) const {
11538 LaneMask &= getSubRegIndexLaneMask(IdxA);
11539 --IdxA; assert(IdxA < 16 && "Subregister index out of bounds");
11540 LaneBitmask Result;
11541 for (const MaskRolOp *Ops = CompositeSequences[IdxA]; Ops->Mask.any(); ++Ops) {
11542 LaneBitmask::Type M = LaneMask.getAsInteger();
11543 if (unsigned S = Ops->RotateLeft)
11544 Result |= LaneBitmask((M >> S) | (M << (LaneBitmask::BitWidth - S)));
11545 else
11546 Result |= LaneBitmask(M);
11547 }
11548 return Result;
11549}
